TEXT.S: Craig Brackins unu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u p'agal tins' tabakiay ayaway mimaliay. Craig Brackins i 2010 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 21, namapili' tu nu Oklahoma City Thunder putiput. 10 bulad 9 demiad, 1987 a mihca, Craig Brackins miunduay.
